Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算今天和他分手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是談了不久就告吹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害了他最重視之人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有他突然逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也沒見面的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我醒來發現他已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣 戀愛總在萌芽時就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為他做的一切 也總是事與願違
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 你真是沒緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有真正被愛過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再喜歡人家 那樣是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在交往的男朋友 悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我對他說喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總是沒什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想結束這單相思的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想把今天的約會作為美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…再也不想有那樣的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打扮得挺漂亮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會嗎 可別遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝蓋沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛在家門口跌倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大的事我什麼都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直在偷窺你哦 約會前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你穿的衣服很適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大不是也打扮了嗎 很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 花了點心思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的不是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號真差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒濕 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個送給他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 還是不想就這樣結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 這樣很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著前面走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不知道他的郵箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您帶來的那位…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是我帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愛的包淋濕了 手機又丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大送我這種怪東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 知道今天是什麼日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是剛剛接到聯繫的山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿到你的手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 順便給你送來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不請自來會不會給你造成麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也不知道工作什麼時候能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面碰頭比較困難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻煩您特地送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口有點渴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請我喝點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你男朋友有打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有留言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 好像搞錯把小型驢裝進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫小型驢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:13:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 給我打…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個無可救藥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優柔寡斷 膽小怕事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又傻傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你更讓人覺得可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 好像還什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢 停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 再見一次面確認下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓悠大嚇一大跳 所以要乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鈴聲是悠大打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機掉了 所以沒法跟你聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那個盒子裡裝著一個叫小型驢的動物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 裝著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有胡鬧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這個人是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天不是也和男人在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆不是在耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有被真正愛過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…我今天可以早退嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得這麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼把那收拾乾淨你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嗎 你住在前男友那了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是了 提不上前男友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像有個女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不能很好表達自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法表達愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想我這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛美希哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…昨天的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成悠大也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有恐高症啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去東京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機師傅 請開快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很危險 你小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 你別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我那麼任性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給悠大的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我找回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太危險 快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是 想著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是在打工還是在家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是不由自主地會想你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你想像的那種人

Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:20.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの時の２人輝いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この恋は永遠と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕の隣りには君がもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君のとなりには僕はもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:32.46,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今まで見たことない泣き顔を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:36.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕は君の手を握ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:42.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を離せばもう逢えないよ 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔で別れたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:46.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}から言う マタアイマショウ マタアイマショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の前では強く優しく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頼られたかったよまさしく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けず嫌い 強がる芝居
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最後の最後も素直になれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの言葉に涙し 涙し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:01.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを言葉で励まし 励まし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:03.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}言葉の魔法はもうすぐ 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いい思い出となって消え去る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.52,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そして傷つけたことは謝らない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:11.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「でもありがとう」これ以上は言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目的地なんてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:15.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たどり着いたのあなたの優しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:17.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はそんなに強くない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:20.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悲しみ我慢してるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣いてもいいよ 僕も泣くから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:25.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日だけは許してよ神様
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.28,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:32.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今まで見たことない泣き顔を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:36.49,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕は君の手を握ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:42.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を離せばもう逢えないよ 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔で別れたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}から言う マタアイマショウ マタアイマショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:51.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いろんな人に愛されて 常にあなたはまぶしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.26,0:23:54.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だから嫉妬し ケンカし 涙し
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:56.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}これからはもう それも出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}お互い違う人好きになって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:01.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}お互い違う人生歩んで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「僕はとっても幸せでした」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:06.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私もとっても幸せでした」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:08.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか心からいなくなるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:11.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だからしたいよ 素晴らしい過去に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:13.57,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この恋を未来に誇れます
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:15.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙まみれ 笑顔でめくる明日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:18.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしてまずこの場で別れ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:20.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わかってる きっと逢うことないって
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:05.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気持ちはわりきれないよ 簡単に
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.36,0:25:11.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}反対にその思いを大切にすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.16,0:25:14.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}整理が出来るまで思えばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.71,0:25:17.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}会えなくて そばにいなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.75,0:25:20.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思うだけ 忘れないことだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.17,0:25:22.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.28,0:25:26.63,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと過ごした大切な日々
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.66,0:25:31.37,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この僕を優しく包んでくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:37.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}でも明日からはもう逢えないよ 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.10,0:25:40.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生まれ変わっても必ずマタアイマショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.20,0:25:46.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今まで見たことない泣き顔を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.60,0:25:50.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕は君の手を握ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.55,0:25:56.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を離せばもう逢えないよ 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.37,0:25:57.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔で別れたい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.85,0:26:01.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}から言う マタアイマショウ マタアイマショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.73,0:26:06.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と僕と
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.53,0:26:12.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悲しい別れがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.76,0:26:15.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}楽しいとき笑えるよな
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.24,0:26:17.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}逃げ出さず現実を受け止めた
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.82,0:26:20.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もちろん君に出会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:20.01,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾經以為我們兩人之間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.47,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永恆不變的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.86,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如今我的身旁已不再有你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.01,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}而你的身旁我已…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:32.46,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看著從未見過的哭泣臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:36.31,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我握著你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:42.17,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦放開手 就再也見不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.76,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望帶著笑容與你分手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:46.94,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我說「擇日再相逢」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.41,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望在你面前既堅強又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.73,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能讓你依賴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.14,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我裝出好勝又逞強的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.35,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}到最後的最後都無法坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.82,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為你的話語而流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:01.30,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用話語給你鼓勵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:03.33,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼看言語的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.69,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}馬上就要變成美好回憶 消失而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.52,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}對於傷害你的事不說道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:11.00,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但要對你說聲謝謝 僅止於此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.76,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}原本就沒有目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:15.27,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我最後找到的是你的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:17.73,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你並沒有那麼堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:20.30,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是不是強忍住悲傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.64,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}哭出來吧 我也會一起哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:25.17,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望上天原諒我們今天的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.28,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:32.56,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看著從未見過的哭泣臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:36.49,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我握著你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:42.18,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦放開手 就再也見不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.64,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望帶著笑容與你分手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.90,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我說「擇日再相逢」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:51.25,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被許多人愛著的你 總是那麼耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.26,0:23:54.24,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我嫉妒 吵架 流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:56.44,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可是從今以後 這也成了奢望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.81,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此愛上不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:01.32,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}踏上不同的人生道路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.22,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我很幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:06.08,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我也很幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:08.53,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也許哪天會從彼此的心中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:11.11,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我寧願把它當成一段美好的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:13.57,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與你的相戀是我未來的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:15.84,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我願淚流滿面的走向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:18.08,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於是我們此時在這裡分別
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:20.70,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中也知道一定不會再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:05.24,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}感情並非那麼容易就能割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.36,0:25:11.15,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}反而不如將它留作珍貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.16,0:25:14.69,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在整理好心情之前 想起你也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.71,0:25:17.74,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不能見面 不在身邊也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.75,0:25:20.17,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要想著就好 更不會遺忘…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.17,0:25:22.27,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.28,0:25:26.63,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾經與你一起度過那段珍貴的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.66,0:25:31.37,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}給了一個將我溫柔包容的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:37.09,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不過明天開始就不能與你相見
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.10,0:25:40.95,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望我們來生還能再相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.20,0:25:46.60,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看著從未見過的哭泣臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.60,0:25:50.54,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我握著你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.55,0:25:56.35,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦放開手 就再也見不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.37,0:25:57.81,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望帶著笑容與你分手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.85,0:26:01.19,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我說「擇日再相逢」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.73,0:26:06.04,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.53,0:26:12.70,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}正因為有悲傷的離別
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.76,0:26:15.22,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今後才有歡樂的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.24,0:26:17.82,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我毫不猶豫的接受了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.82,0:26:20.51,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}過與你的相遇依舊是我一生的幸福


